Okay.

17:49.460 --> 17:52.340
I think the next picture we have is you as a young Marine.

17:52.340 --> 17:53.340
There you are.

17:53.340 --> 17:55.940
Was that when you just joined up?

17:55.940 --> 17:57.940
And just got out of boot camp.

17:57.940 --> 18:00.020
Just got out of boot camp.

