19:21.020 --> 19:22.020
Right.

19:22.020 --> 19:30.900
Because they were killers, murderers, rapists, thieves.

19:30.900 --> 19:33.260
So they tried.

19:33.260 --> 19:43.540
We were able to severely knock out seven infrared visions of the Chinese.

19:43.540 --> 19:48.580
And they had a few more that got out.

19:48.580 --> 19:49.580
Right.

19:49.580 --> 19:50.580
There's some more photographs.

19:50.580 --> 19:53.340
You talked about this photograph, you're in the middle.

